    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. Not because i look different, but because the person who actually lived, the one with the dreams and the spark... they died a long time ago. I feel like i'm just a walking corpse. Just an empty shell going through the motions of a life that ended years ago.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
