      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way, but the \"you\" left behind isn't gone forever; it's just resting in a quiet space waiting to be found again. You don't have to force yourself to feel alive right now, but remember that the person who died was carrying a heavy load, and you are free to let it drop without guilt. The space you occupy isn't wasted; it's simply the room where your true self can finally start breathing again.",
